{"tid":322260,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"純分享：請珍惜保護牙齒","createTime":"2017-07-14T16:13:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-24T08:19:24.000Z","uid":5218,"like":4,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"49315a3ad33a139aa966255f56cdb0d3c582fdce","tid":322260,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:13:48.000Z","msg":"上月尾左邊智慧齒同右邊上犬齒附近牙肉含膿發炎引至牙痛痛到半夜頂唔順要食止痛藥同敷冰先可以禁襟得住啲痛，食咗一個星期消炎丸但情況冇好轉，而且呢段時間食唔到野咁濟，最後鼓起勇氣去睇牙醫，牙醫係我家姐介紹，去到俾佢check同照X光後話我嘅左邊智慧齒本身位置生得唔夠直有少少斜生形成空隙一般刷牙刷唔到導致蛀牙細菌滋生從而發炎，第一次佢先幫我清左發炎牙肉內既膿，而右犬齒含膿原因係因為佢清膿其間發現有一粒好細既核攝左向犬齒底部引至發炎含膿，等發炎好返後再去比佢剝埋右下既智慧齒同補返總共七隻牙，其中左右兩邊大牙蛀到好深但好彩未到神經所以唔駛杜牙根，而上方有兩隻門牙亦因為牙週病底部開始蛀，一次整返好棚牙感覺好似重生一樣，如果唔係呢次牙痛再唔理可能到時情況仲麻煩<br />\n<br />\n因為小學期間 d 牙科保健既陰影攪到好怕再去睇牙醫，但今次清含膿同剝智慧齒除左打麻醉藥拮𠴱下有有 d 感覺外過程其實都唔覺得話特別痛，呢個牙醫 d 手勢確係唔錯，而且佢可以將我既緊張同焦慮減至最低。"},{"pid":"4fce89eea4cc6936850f5daab987631ebdb9485a","tid":322260,"uid":29523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:14:33.000Z","msg":"too long<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c98b5518871486ab388709b1785ea218a55fec68","tid":322260,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:16:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>too long<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本來仲長，我已減左好多。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"987190bfba2708bc217c5628e6d4be87dba44816","tid":322260,"uid":16399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:16:17.000Z","msg":"諗起整牙都覺得痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 準備杜牙根"},{"pid":"986ee98065033a872f12ce03b0533fd2e1e7281b","tid":322260,"uid":1139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:16:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"994f85974a8198c4a39d2fdebf5ecfcf74571d48","tid":322260,"uid":61989,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:17:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f672e5802b814016b5057d15ccc974c57a779e9a","tid":322260,"uid":1139,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:17:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2de407959ac4c555cc2d84e1215ac88ab6a38a40","tid":322260,"uid":29523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:17:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>too long<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n重點：<br />\n牙肉含膿發炎引至牙痛<br />\n痛到半夜頂唔順<br />\n要食止痛藥同敷冰先可以禁襟得住啲痛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nThanks"},{"pid":"44c9a105623fb01afb47ddf28796639300322a40","tid":322260,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:28:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>too long<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n重點：<br />\n牙肉含膿發炎引至牙痛<br />\n痛到半夜頂唔順<br />\n要食止痛藥同敷冰先可以禁襟得住啲痛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nThanks</blockquote><br />\n痛到天光，之前都未試過痛成咁，痛到向屋度週圍行。"},{"pid":"996f6638a52663d5b3e0d6fefae61f0905b1baab","tid":322260,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:31:56.000Z","msg":"我都3x啦<br />\n上兩星期去牙醫又係好scare<br />\n同你一樣細個陰影"},{"pid":"d11fa4f9549be5b442cc9121f2cc73e4973d7da8","tid":322260,"uid":4574,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:32:38.000Z","msg":"請善用分段及標點符號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1682f12e4d11815dcb27043e38b1bb29301061cc","tid":322260,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:32:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起整牙都覺得痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 準備杜牙根</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好彩我剝𠴱隻智慧齒唔駛開刀，全程係 feel 到醫生用力咁扯，扯左四五下都好似扯唔甩我仲擔心緊佢會唔會割開 d 牙肉，諗緊時原來佢已經剝左出黎。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d8dba21624405f47afda573b0836053911b6d43","tid":322260,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:34:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都3x啦<br />\n上兩星期去牙醫又係好scare<br />\n同你一樣細個陰影</blockquote><br />\n係，以前真係比佢地攪到以後都唔敢再睇牙醫。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c5ead6000829f5d1b3201bb29ccee41f7e43cd9","tid":322260,"uid":119450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:34:57.000Z","msg":"正常成年人每日刷兩次牙根本冇可能蛀牙<br />\n<br />\n好心你顧掂自己先啦柒頭"},{"pid":"793ddffdb254813de0ac115e2faec968cdf103e7","tid":322260,"uid":71840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:34:59.000Z","msg":"請問用咗幾錢？"},{"pid":"d1979685ec2302c5973e233721bcf2d4d3756957","tid":322260,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:35:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請善用分段及標點符號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09fe9dacbaa5bffde3740f6d5293a81bd7f7b125","tid":322260,"uid":73160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:36:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都3x啦<br />\n上兩星期去牙醫又係好scare<br />\n同你一樣細個陰影</blockquote><br />\n係，以前真係比佢地攪到以後都唔敢再睇牙醫。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無用牙線<br />\n<br />\n3x 年一次都無用過"},{"pid":"d4965060867dc144c6f71c8f4c8e594eeda64ade","tid":322260,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:39:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正常成年人每日刷兩次牙根本冇可能蛀牙<br />\n<br />\n好心你顧掂自己先啦柒頭</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我早晚都會刷牙，但平時經常鍾意飲 d 酸野，大大支漱口水同牙線擺向度又唔用，自今次之後真係唔敢唔用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96be8bac60ab4b0717dce5348cbcbb7e8ce403a9","tid":322260,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:40:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>請問用咗幾錢？</blockquote><br />\n總共八千左右。"},{"pid":"99610e9f44a888f1cc3da376c86c9d81acd0ad61","tid":322260,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:44:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>我都3x啦<br />\n上兩星期去牙醫又係好scare<br />\n同你一樣細個陰影</blockquote><br />\n係，以前真係比佢地攪到以後都唔敢再睇牙醫。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無用牙線<br />\n<br />\n3x 年一次都無用過</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好少會用，有時夜晚向梳化恰著恰到四五點先再刷牙上床，咁已經死得。"},{"pid":"38155ec5598f531a4106d5f2b9457a061992439c","tid":322260,"uid":58670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:44:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我都3x啦<br />\n上兩星期去牙醫又係好scare<br />\n同你一樣細個陰影</blockquote><br />\n係，以前真係比佢地攪到以後都唔敢再睇牙醫。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我睇親牙醫去之前都會胃痛同頭痛，連去洗牙都會係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fffac38c65c5878e736d6a7127929fef7b4cfe13","tid":322260,"uid":19926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:45:53.000Z","msg":"想知牙醫係邊個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13c57427b6c8dabbe55c45cfd429747905d988e9","tid":322260,"uid":25028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T16:47:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正常成年人每日刷兩次牙根本冇可能蛀牙<br />\n<br />\n好心你顧掂自己先啦柒頭</blockquote><br />\n咁d牙醫就唔會開到周圍都係啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b33d7ab71952489fa9f47c96e85f0571c997964e","tid":322260,"uid":124506,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T17:31:40.000Z","msg":"想知係邊個牙醫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68d398b7cdc0bd6444d07fee6720e5d5f21ab611","tid":322260,"uid":107603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T17:37:14.000Z","msg":"補完明唔明顯睇得出？"},{"pid":"5a7e031a766c71cb5b2f4f7fe8eac14b4ba4aba5","tid":322260,"uid