"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T13:58:00.000Z","msg":"上月尾到而家食既全部都係皮蛋瘦肉粥同餐肉湯通粉，食到慣左返唔到轉到頭。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef575eb6522c6b587acdb656136acaadb40f3dd","tid":322260,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T13:58:57.000Z","msg":"想知樓主有無註過牙？"},{"pid":"b2cdcd771c0b4ee66e812e903b085f85fa935eec","tid":322260,"uid":124741,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T14:06:15.000Z","msg":"諗起細個因為懶夜晚唔刷牙 真係好ON9"},{"pid":"57cfdecfe21ca58047fafcf2c19aa821fc0d65f8","tid":322260,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T14:13:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗起細個因為懶夜晚唔刷牙 真係好ON9</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我廿零歲都有段時間夜晚懶刷牙，直至到有一次牙肉發炎後就改變返夜晚刷牙習慣。"},{"pid":"6c33f8ead1127b115af664bcd4630c0ce0f56d2f","tid":322260,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T14:24:26.000Z","msg":"牙線係必須用架啦<br />\n<br />\n刷牙真係刷唔乾淨<br />\n<br />\n本身刷牙兩隻字都好鬼誤導<br />\n<br />\n刷牙仲要刷牙肉，牙肉根本好易發炎<br />\n<br />\n攪到人人都有牙周病有牙血"},{"pid":"badb1ea46233fbbdabee9e6e7a582a42e4a77c7c","tid":322260,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T14:25:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>補完明唔明顯睇得出？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n完全同正常冇分別，唔似以前銀汞合金補完會有銀灰色印。"},{"pid":"e04c8c2540fb3b6851519aa9903efb00912276aa","tid":322260,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T14:26:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>牙線係必須用架啦<br />\n<br />\n刷牙真係刷唔乾淨<br />\n<br />\n本身刷牙兩隻字都好鬼誤導<br />\n<br />\n刷牙仲要刷牙肉，牙肉根本好易發炎<br />\n<br />\n攪到人人都有牙周病有牙血</blockquote><br />\n以前細路教𠴱套方法真係累死人。"},{"pid":"0b1a7f0cb5fbb8165649402ee625419a540e7394","tid":322260,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T14:27:26.000Z","msg":"同埋每年去牙醫洗一次牙真係基本黎"},{"pid":"18843c76294b1d64deb46f9b4137ac16aaba286a","tid":322260,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T14:29:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>牙線係必須用架啦<br />\n<br />\n刷牙真係刷唔乾淨<br />\n<br />\n本身刷牙兩隻字都好鬼誤導<br />\n<br />\n刷牙仲要刷牙肉，牙肉根本好易發炎<br />\n<br />\n攪到人人都有牙周病有牙血</blockquote><br />\n以前細路教𠴱套方法真係累死人。</blockquote><br />\n好多人都去到牙肉萎縮左好多先知發覺<br />\n<br />\n到最後牙同牙中間既空位已經好大<br />\n<br />\n大牙縫刷都zip得入<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/16.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8234bb29f9f6467749ae3a81bbbace02a65c657","tid":322260,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T14:32:14.000Z","msg":"同埋上一代唔識牙肉牙週病問題都好影響<br />\n<br />\n見你有牙血同你講熱氣<br />\n<br />\n佢地完全唔知係牙週病<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile_big.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實去洗牙 日日勤用番牙線已經可以改善非常多"},{"pid":"202470728c35d31c1811b704899beed120f63eaa","tid":322260,"uid":5218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T14:36:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同埋每年去牙醫洗一次牙真係基本黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢次我真係覺悟，個醫生問我對上一次睇牙醫係幾時既事，我好細聲話三年級，佢都好驚訝話唔係掛。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3648002dff91334a62705a3c83c83035a9c91ddc","tid":322260,"uid":64271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T14:44:26.000Z","msg":"好撚驚睇牙醫，有3隻牙蛀得好嚴重，試過痛到hihi頂唔順，去到牙科門口都唔敢入去，最後死忍爛忍唔痛就冇理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de866ab0d87baba1339e5a97220c586fbe3222bf","tid":322260,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T14:45:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚驚睇牙醫，有3隻牙蛀得好嚴重，試過痛到hihi頂唔順，去到牙科門口都唔敢入去，最後死忍爛忍唔痛就冇理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲後生喎<br />\n唔係咁快想好似老人家咁 鍍牙根下"},{"pid":"336f8cd990d8155f3f86d487182419f17d09aadb","tid":322260,"uid":36701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T14:49:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好撚驚睇牙醫，有3隻牙蛀得好嚴重，試過痛到hihi頂唔順，去到牙科門口都唔敢入去，最後死忍爛忍唔痛就冇理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你覺得痛應該蛀到好深下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n小心好似我咁要杜牙根<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0befd87c26ffaa802b762e7dcecf0f4a777fba6c","tid":322260,"uid":26361,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T14:50:43.000Z","msg":"今日剝左牙 痛到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e66d0e673e58b6f6db10cbc4025a8981c742d67a","tid":322260,"uid":808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T15:03:41.000Z","msg":"巴打睇你情況應該都係有牙周病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之前我都有呢個問題，最煩就係每次刷牙都流牙血，<br />\n之後去睇牙醫照x光，深層洗牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 要打麻醉針果隻，持續咗三四年，<br />\n情況先有改善，而家刷牙冇再流血，唔洗keep住睇牙醫。<br />\n但有牙周病手尾都好長，唔單止要格三四個月洗牙，做好個人護理先最重要<br />\n牙線，牙縫刷一定要用。<br />\n伸利：全程用公務員牙醫福利，如果唔係醫療費都幾甘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"141a486b6eceb38d5b3e06403643c02774645895","tid":322260,"uid":65439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T15:11:46.000Z","msg":"我都超懶 有時個排心情唔好就唔刷牙<br />\n由細到大都係咁 d fd既牙好白好乾淨<br />\n我就隻隻牙都有d黑色線同積<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有冇方法變返哂白同健康d<br />\n<br />\nbtw 對上一次洗牙 個牙醫又話冇乜事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}